videos.headline: Rowland rumbles for six
videos.description: Tennessee RB Seth Rowland rushes for a 4-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Manning connects with Werts for long play
videos.description: Georgia State QB Conner Manning completes a pass to WR Ari Werts for a 59-yard gain.

videos.headline: Rowland finds space for big gain
videos.description: Tennessee State RB Seth Rowland breaks free for a 59-yard rush.

videos.headline: Winchester links up with Bateman for TD
videos.description: Georgia State QB Aaron Winchester completes a 36-yard pass to Taz Bateman for a  touchdown.

videos.headline: Tigers force another turnover
videos.description: Tennessee State DE Ebenezer Ogundeko recovers a fumble forced by DE Dell Porter

videos.headline: Nesbeth closes the game
videos.description: Tennessee State CB Dajour Nesbeth intercepts Georgia State QB Aaron Winchester to seal the win.

videos.headline: Harris' performance the difference maker
videos.description: Matt Stewart and Wayne Gandy recap the stellar performance by Treon Harris and the miscues that led to the Tigers winning 17-10.
